{"tid":541254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【火燒高鐵】安徽列車行駛中起火冒濃煙 1400客冒雪驚逃","createTime":"2018-01-26T08:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T08:52:23.000Z","uid":65864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a91cfe5e25ccca2a99a76bd6e43a9e377ad4a649","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"[本報訊] 今日一列從山東青島開往浙江杭州的高鐵，行駛至安徽省滁州市期間，第二節車廂着火，火勢相當猛烈，列車在暴雪中緊急在當地的定遠縣停車，1,400名乘客慌張逃生，紛紛爬上月台。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是G281次列車，有列車上的乘客指出今日約11時半，列車行駛時車廂便着火冒煙，但列車的人員沒有馬上停車，而是繼續開行至定遠站才疏散乘客。現場拍到的片段顯示，高鐵冒出濃濃黑煙，更冒出火光。<br />\n<br />\n鐵道部門指出，這列高鐵有16個車廂，共載有1,400人，事故是2號車廂的電器設備發生故障冒煙，事故未造成傷亡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1f7252c57c42904abf4f49fd49dbf0c46aea1d","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"37fba24ba36ae42d834e643f273e2d55b392155d","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d15469ec4031de5521a08c7b41e631da5b568759","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9ae307d59e21db4c116f60891e776db547730eb2","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f7a9ed8306a6aa51db2b09dbd8b35d0bfd117acb","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"880effc471c159f4cdecb1e13518267a92321598","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"6caa35a8b7a6545bbbe578eed69b18eb4dee41f3","tid":541254,"uid":65864,"like":0,